OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"Schools should also be given a
OL,8,Fstronger statutory role in driving
OL,9,Fmulti-agency working, with powers to
OL,10,Fconvene, co-ordinate and lead meetings
OL,11,Fwhere appropriate."
OL,13,FParents in England face higher fines
OL,14,Fif they take their children out of
OL,15,Fclass without permission this year as
OL,16,Fpart of a Government drive to boost
OL,17,Fattendance since the pandemic.
