OL,4,Cforced to co-operate with schools `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FBut the report said teachers currently
OL,8,Fcannot compel parents to attend
OL,9,Fmeetings if they have concerns about
OL,10,Ftheir child's behaviour.
OL,12,FAlexander Iosad, acting director of
OL,13,Fgovernment innovation at TBI, said:
OL,14,F"Today's report shows that teachers
OL,15,Fare powerless and unsupported to
OL,16,Ftackle a rising epidemic of disruptive
OL,17,Fand dangerous behaviour.
OL,19,F"We must shift the balance of
OL,20,Fauthority back in favour of teachers
OL,21,Fand give them the support they need."
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@AOU}D@eO]
