OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FHe added: "Let's be clear; this is not
OL,8,Fjust a challenge, it is a safeguarding
OL,9,Fissue.
OL,11,F"Schools should therefore become
OL,12,Fstatutory partners in safeguarding and
OL,13,Fshould have the authority to compel
OL,14,Fparents and other agencies like the
OL,15,Fpolice, NHS and social services to
OL,16,Fcome together and agree an action plan.
