OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"Only by giving teachers the power to
OL,8,Faddress poor behaviour not just in the
OL,9,Fclassroom but at its source will we be
OL,10,Fable to keep teachers in the
OL,11,Fprofession."
OL,13,FPepe Di'Iasio, general secretary of
OL,14,Fthe Association of School and College
OL,15,FLeaders (ASCL), said many schools are
OL,16,F"experiencing challenging behaviour"
OL,17,Ffrom students and the issue appears to
OL,18,Fhave worsened since the pandemic "when
OL,19,Fnormal behaviours and routines were
OL,20,Fdisrupted".
